# .awakenedignore
# Extra ignore layer for the awakened agent's file search (glob/grep/tree).
# Same syntax as .gitignore. Applied ON TOP of .gitignore via ripgrep --ignore-file.
# Purpose: keep the agent focused on real source, away from generated/vendored noise.
# Use `!pattern` to re-include something. Edit freely per project.

# Dependencies & package manager noise
node_modules/
.bun/
bun.lock
bun.lockb
package-lock.json
pnpm-lock.yaml
yarn.lock
.pnp.*
vendor/

